{
  "stem": "27767.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were two lagers-- a new lager, and an old, old camp lager, they called it, concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And a new one and old one, we were in the new one.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All together, I understand there were 6,000 Jews at that time-- I mean slaves there in the-- in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were put there in a barrack.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I think my barrack, I think it was number one, if I remember good, number ten.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the capo was a German, which was a German criminal.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He-- he was taken into that camp, because he killed, I understand, some of his family.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he had a black stripe, which means he was a criminal-- a criminal in that jail, in that camp actually.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Oh, I forgot to tell you, in Auschwitz, we got a number.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were not tattooed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We got a number on-- my number was 4,321.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my father's was 4,320.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that number was put on my yellow star.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Plus, on the head, we had a stripe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And plus, on the back of my jacket, there was also a big yellow stripe.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You should be recognized, if you tried to escape or something, anyplace.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the barrack in Warsaw?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Warsaw, there it was better, because we-- we had, like, double-- triple banks, a bank with triple beds.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And each of us had a bank, one bank, one bed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I slept.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remembered my father slept on the bottom.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I slept in the middle, and on top somebody else.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we didn't have pillows there either.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we used our boots.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we had a-- we got a blanket, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we ate in the-- we ate in the barracks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We got-- actually, only in the evening and in the morning.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
